  "description": "This nighttime photograph showcases a vibrant city skyline reflected in dark, rippling water. The cityscape is dominated by numerous tall buildings, illuminated with a multitude of colorful lights \u2013 primarily yellows, oranges, and reds.  Some buildings are brightly lit with white lights, while others feature vibrant accents of blue and red. The lights create a festive and energetic atmosphere. A wake or trail of water is visible in the foreground, suggesting the photograph was taken from a moving vessel.  The sky is a deep, dark blue, providing a strong contrast to the bright city lights. The composition captures a sense of movement and energy with a strong focus on urban illumination.",
